<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Andres Steinpachs
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vormals <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie wol das ist, daz
                        er vast und <expan>swerlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns getan hat, als ewr edel
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> mag
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Doch ew czü eren und gevallnüzz wolt er
                        uns abnemen und pesserung tün und, daz ir uns das an
                            <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> brief <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schribt</expan>,
                        so <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darauf <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ein
                        antwurt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und also wer es, daz
                        ir uns noch <add>in <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>kurcze<ex>n</ex></expan> czeit</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schribt</expan> daz er das tün wolt, <add>so
                                    <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir das durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen nemen nach rate und ein czeit
                            ein gütlich steen und einen <add><expan>frewntliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gelege<ex>n</ex>liche<ex>n</ex></expan></add> tag aufnemen,
                            und <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> cze reden. Wan etc.</add> wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dinst
                            <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>sunderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Urba<ex>n</ex>i</expan>.</ab>
</div>
